      "title": "<span id=\"#13477\" class=\"scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold flex items-center\"><h1 class=\"inline !mb-1 scroll-m-16 text-3xl font-bold\">announce</h1><div class=\"pl-2 flex-1 text-textSecondary text-xl font-serif\">(v.)</div></span>",
      "html": "<p>约于1500年，“宣布，正式公布”，源自古法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">anoncier</span> “宣布，公告”（12世纪，现代法语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">annoncer</span>），源自拉丁语 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">annuntiare</span>， <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">adnuntiare</span> “宣布，公布”，字面意思为“带来消息”，由 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">ad</span> “到”（见 <a href=\"/cn/word/ad-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of ad- \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">ad-</a>)和 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">nuntiare</span> “叙述，报告”组成，源自 <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">nuntius</span> “信使”（源自 PIE 词根 <a href=\"/cn/word/*neu-\" title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of *neu- \" rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"crossreference notranslate\">*neu-</a> “喊叫”）。相关词汇： <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">Announced</span>； <span class=\"foreign notranslate\">announcing</span>。</p><ins class=\"adsbygoogle relative inline-block transition-all inline-block h-[250px] w-[300px]\" data-ad-slot=\"4000736339\" data-adtest=\"off\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\"></ins>"
    }
